text: "Red High Heels" is the first single by American singer-songwriter Kellie Pickler. ==Music video== The music video for "Red High Heels" was directed by Chris Hicky. The video premiered on October 26, 2006 on CMT. The video debuted at number 18 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of January 11, 2007. ==References== Category:2006 songs Category:Debut singles Category:BNA Records singles Category:Kellie Pickler songs
